Class SynsetRelationGenerator

    This class is used for extraction of synset-relations, defined in Uby-LMF, out of WordNet's data.

                       LexicalEntryGenerator lexicalEntryGenerator)
        Constructs an instance of SynsetRelationGenerator based on the consumed parameters.

        synsetGenerator - an instance of SynsetGenerator used for accessing generated Uby-LMF synsets.
        lexicalEntryGenerator - an instance of LexicalEntryGenerator used for accessing generated LexicalEntry-instances.
